Rehearing Denied.

No. 561. No. 657. No. 666. Standard Commercial Tobacco Co. et al. v. Snyder, Secretary of the Treasury, et al., ante, p. 918; Holmes et al. v. United States et al., ante, p. 927; and Monolith Portland Midwest Co. v. Reconstruction Finance Corp., ante, p. 932.

The petitions for rehearing in these cases are severally denied.
